## 命令行
1. Clone仓库到本地：```
git clone <repository url>
```
* 建立新的分支并切换到该分支：```git checkout -b <branch name>```

* 提交代码：```git add * ``` ```git commit -m <commit message>```
* 推送到远程分支：```git push origin <branch name>```

* 与客户端一样，发起pull request
